Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you did a really great job.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They woulda gotten nowhere without me and Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty funny coming from {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.59,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, this is truly amazing.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very impressed.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We all worked really hard.{#1}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more fun than I thought it'd be, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Well, I'd say this calls for popsicles!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.10,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My treat!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want {replace}Gori Gori{Gori-Gori-kun} pops or Home{Keep this comment: Possible hyphen here, but whatever. I definitely don't approve of making nonexistent closed compounds, though.} Base Bars?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So cheap!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, {replace}Teach{Sensei}, it's too cold for popsicles today anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We even canceled swimming 'cause of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have a point.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.22,0:02:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But sadly, they don't sell meat buns around this time of year.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.45,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do the Boatdrift Ceremony...{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.41,0:02:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{They said that }Completely in sync.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot damn!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you two close!{maybe more like "how romantic!" or something, but its sarcastic, so...}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They've totally got the hots for each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.84,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.27,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, no need to play dumb.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far they've gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.53,0:02:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That hurt...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a lot more than I thought it would.{the jp is purposefully vague to coincide with their teasing}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in a way, we're already doing the ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it how {you taught us }they did it long ago...
