Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with people from both the sea and the surface working together.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we do it that way?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a great idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.50,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, after putting in so much effort, it'd be nice to see a real Boatdrift Ceremony!{#2}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But for that to happen, we'd need help from Shioshishio,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and that might be a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.88,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're gonna do it anyway, we should do it right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you guys agree?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I mean, we've already come this far.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I really do...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the disagreements between Shioshishio {Village }and the Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{they say }it's not happening this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent so much time and effort making everything,{#3}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's do it! A real Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai— Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about Shishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.08,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu, you take lead{,} and figure \Nsomething out on the Oshiooshi end{ of things}.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're set on this, but things may get rough.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, but it's just...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna do this halfheartedly, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be hopeless, but I don't wanna leave behind any regrets just 'cause we didn't try.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Count me in!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu, you too, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me neither.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why not!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is terrific!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an9}This is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.28,0:04:18.92,Alternative,,0,250,0,,{\an9}Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what youth's all about!{PV}{Carpe diem, guys! Carpe diem!}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll help out as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this, everyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure we get to do the Boatdrift Ceremony, no matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll grant your and Tsumugu's wish.{this is the same sentence as two lines earlier, just flipped in the jp}
