Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this year's Boatdrift Ceremony a reality!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us {get enough signatures }by signing one of these forms!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're definitely not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's make this year's Boatdrift Ceremony a reality!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please help us out!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us o—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just gonna scare 'em off like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to do the Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Boatdrift Ceremony...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better. Just keep that up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.63,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're part of Hama Middle School's {"}Association to Make the Boatdrift Ceremony a Reality.{"}{}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they weren't doing it this year, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're volunteers from \NHama Middle School.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to make the ceremony even bigger than last year's!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you kids can handle it by yourselves?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign this!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you,{technical comma splice. Added for flow} we're serious about this.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since you asked so nicely.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari's {sort of }amazing today.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.44,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he so worked up over this?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably going all out in order to distract himself from something{his frustrations}.{his efforts are a way to distract himself from his frustration regarding manaka}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think he had such a competitive side to him.{he seemed to me competitive from the start...}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there's more to people than meets the eye.{theres a lot more to someone than meets the eye}{"Autobots wage their battle to destroy the evil forces of the Decepticons."}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am! Pardon me, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you possibly spare me a moment of your time?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I suppose if it's just for a moment...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there {\i1}is{\i0} more to people than meets the eye.{yep, theres a lot more to someone than meets the eye}{they dont think of whathisface as the ladies man that he apparently is}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to work harder, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing the Boatdrift Ceremony...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that {really }suits you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that really matter, though?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. I mean, people can \Nonly do what's within their capacity{ to do}.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you try too hard to do something that's not in your capacity, you only wind up hurting yourself.{she herself is hurt by trying things shes not good at / everyone is hurt themselves}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are really going at it, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari{-san}, thank you for talking to the manager for us.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even mention it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.24,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Sayama{-kun} is the manager's son, and he's helping out too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.71,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I'd like to see a real Boatdrift Ceremony myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, could you put these on display in the store?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give me some of those forms, \NI'll be sure to get you some signatures, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me some as well?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hand them out to some people I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.42,0:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, getting the people of the surface and sea to work hand in hand...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that matters to me {on a personal level }too.{the literal jp is "i cant think of it as some strangers problem}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I want to do the Boatdrift Ceremony...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make it happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how many signatures we got!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you at least {\i1}try{\i0} talking to the fishing association?
