Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.23,0:07:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how many {signatures }you got.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.54,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They{Oshiooshi} were the ones who said they wouldn't do it this year in the first place.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time Hikari's ever seriously asked you for anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of parent would you be if you didn't at least listen?{It wouldn't hurt you to at least listen to him.}{This may be about hearing out Hikari, or it may be about actually trying to listen to the people of Oshiooshi, so I'm going to leave "listen" as is.}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw them collecting signatures earlier myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all working so hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.46,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of the surface won't listen.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in talking to them.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.22,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the guys on the surface were all pigs at first, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there was no point in talking to 'em.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.97,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, they thought of us as fish,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which made us even.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were all wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not fish, and they're not pigs!{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all people! And we can \Ncommunicate with each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.96,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're serious about this!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you only try once,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,please get everyone together{,} and try talking to them!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need my help, do you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, forget I even asked!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay out of our way, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything went okay with the fishery cooperative?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that hard, actually.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{For flow. Actually part of following sentence, obviously.}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they didn't say much about the Boatdrift Ceremony{ themselves},
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was on their minds the whole time.{they didnt mention the boatdrift ceremony themselves (after he brought it up) but it (the cooperation with the sea) was on their minds (during the discussion)}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So how'd it go on your end?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My stupid dad wouldn't listen,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Men's Club heard me out.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.58,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell them that the people of the surface have agreed already,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it'll work out{ somehow}.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's finally showtime{, then}!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do the Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but first, it's time for food!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I really hope everything works out.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't eat before, there won't be any time to hang out after.{to hang out after school}{maybe after the ceremony?}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But they all seem so stubborn...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch. I'm gonna make this happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari's really putting his all into this, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, he seems sort of... um...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,different now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Different?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, I know Hii{-kun} always does his best,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.88,0:09:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but, um... it's just that it seems different{ somehow} this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.70,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...{your determination to finish your sentences didn't last long}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he's trying to change.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Change?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want things to change.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I want us all to stay together forever.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Change?! That's not good!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to {hurry and}try to stop him somehow!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop him and undo it!{It's time to stop and rewind, To stop and rewind!}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that'll be possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii{-chan}...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.97,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things change whether we want them to or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.57,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once someone decides to change and does everything they can to make it happen,{#5}{check timing}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt even the sea god can stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:39.15,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry342\fscx60\fscy60\c&HFF4C00&\1a&H64&\pos(676,237)\org(665,397)}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they did a pretty good job{ on this}.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impressive.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.48,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not bad at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We may actually be able to use this.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at the detail{ they put in to it}.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they managed to get Hikari's dad to come with them.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm {getting }nervous.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. I kinda need to take a piss.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go instead of telling us about it!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They even prepared offerings.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.32,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We made all that {little }stuff when we were kids, too. Ain't that right, Sakishima?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really make all this yourselves?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.20,0:11:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us and our friends from the surface all worked together.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that explains it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.09,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wooden Maiden's kimono is folded wrong{backwards}.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do, Chii{-chan}?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We sewed it so that the wrong side{left}'s in the front!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wooden Maiden's going to die!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey— }Just calm down!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can fix that in no time.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a preemptive strike.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, it seems everyone's ready now.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the intermediary for today's meeting.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what do all of you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The students put a lot of effort into all this.{#5}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.77,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So as their teacher, I'd really like to see their dream come true.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.96,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like we ever objected to doing the Boatdrift Ceremony to begin with.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, festivals shouldn't be disregarded.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.45,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're not ones to neglect the sea god.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakishima.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids have already done so much.{went so far to do this.}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.16,0:12:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot has happened, \Nbut why don't we just let it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.68,0:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can get started now.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already started, though...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, not {get started }with that.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that we'll hear out your apology now.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apology?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We came all the way here.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to apologize as much as you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hearts are as great{vast/big, but this is cockier, so hehe} as the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.96,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be on the rude side, but we'll hear it out anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do we gotta apologize for?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the ones who didn't wanna do the festival in the first place.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, just wait a sec.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you even remember the last Boatdrift Ceremony?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys kept complainin' about how we didn't have enough money or people,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.86,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so you asked us to scale things down, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and chances are that your complainin' woulda increased every year.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}At that rate,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}if we hadn't been the ones to cancel it,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.05,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, this doesn't look too good, does it?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.22,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}you guys woulda done it yourselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a load of crap!{That's not true!}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here to argue about who should apologize or who's at faul—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt out, kid!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, {\i1}you're{\i0} the ones who {\i1}did{\i0} call it off.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course you should apologize!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason we don't have enough money or people
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is 'cause you guys keep stealin' everything{them}!{the money probably because of overfishing i guess}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.84,0:13:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealin' our fish and our women!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the reason your women keep runnin' off is 'cause you guys aren't dependable?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tryin' to pin the blame on us for that{,} too, are ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.45,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry342\fscx60\fscy60\c&HA33000&\1a&H48&\pos(730,311)\org(719,471)}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's gonna rain.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to come in too?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Hikari dedicated so much time and effort to this,{#6}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do what I can as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.03,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I want to show Miuna{-chan} a real Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of our roots.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.74,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But even aside from that, if Miuna{-chan} ever feels lost,{ever doubts herself / her identity}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.16,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe the memory could be sort of like a beacon of hope in her heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thinking of Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's head in.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you sayin', you fish bastard?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.32,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Excuse us—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up, you pigs!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of your damn squealing!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we settle things once and for all?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you just say?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a bad time?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this sucks.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Itaru{-san}...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about bad timing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You're that punk Akari's seeing!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.24,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn thief!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thie—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got plenty of things we'd like to say to you!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.19,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on here? Hikari! Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you guys give it a break already?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you adults?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you all be civil about this?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay out of the way!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.73,Ceremony999,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HDB&\b1\pos(524,261)\fscx94\fscy94}Looking for \NPart-Timers!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Break up with that guy.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.10,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As Hikari said, we can communicate with each other because we're not fish or pigs.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's {\i1}because{\i0} we can communicate
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.56,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that we realize there are differences \Nbetween us that we can never get over.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.87,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,People of the sea and people of the surface will never see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.57,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought something \Nfelt off when you and I talked.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.11,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I {finally }know what it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.10,0:16:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've been talking about Itaru{-san} and myself this whole time.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.60,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet somehow, you always manage to twist it into being about the sea and the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.91,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago I asked Mom,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why'd you marry Dad?"
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me that the reason was simple.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.79,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She married you because she loved you. \NThat's all there was to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.55,0:17:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So then I decided to ask her,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"What if he'd been from the surface instead?"
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{And then }Mom just smiled at me and said,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.03,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"{Even then, }Your father and I would've been together, no matter what."
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.83,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be Miuna{-chan}'s mother.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay here alone with Dad,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't just sweep our \Ndifferences under the rug.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So she said she was leaving, did she?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The flickering's gotten more pronounced.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't much time left.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, Tomoru?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There any chance you'll reconsider?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is not.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still under my protection, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for all you've done for me,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to live on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming back either!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like being stubborn runs in the family.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do everything in our power.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just give up?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good's gonna come from you{r Correct, but Lord Uroko's got a weird mix of slang-sounding speech.} going {up }to the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone up there who's waiting for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.49,0:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}! Why won't you let us leave?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because }I made a promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.08,0:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I must protect the both of you...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are his descendants.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature's dropping so rapidly.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna freeze at this rate.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.55,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm gonna give up now!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't just be swept along with the current anymore!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My, aren't they persistent.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.76,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, show them mercy.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.59,0:21:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, let's go!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.86,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
